Package: AeroFleet
Type: Package
Title: Aircraft Route Profitability Simulator
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Mohib Usman
Maintainer: Mohib Usman <m.usman2@student.uw.edu.pl>
Description: Simulates the profitability of operating different aircraft types on routes from London Heathrow. Calculates per-flight and daily profit using real-world aircraft specifications, operating costs, ticket prices, and passenger load factors from official aviation sources.
